descriptionHtml:
ECP-PlayerHouse 1
------------------------------------------------
[UPDATE] SORRY FOR NO IMAGES , THE VIDEO IS UPLOADED !
if you\'r a little bit lazy just like me and don\'t want to go all the way to the video\'s tab .. then i got something for yah! : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U22RT88NqwU

first of all , welcome to this mod !
this mod is made by [E.C]Joshua ( steam = jongen603 ) representing Elite Cinema
you can find us at youtube at www.youtube.com/EliteCinemaGaming.

ECP has just started and will have lots of mods , a.t.m. i am working at ECP-WallMart wich is a mod that adds a building with several pretty rich merchants .

back to this mod , 
FEATURES
---------------------------------
EXTERIOR
-Smithing Garden ( grindstone + tanning rack + forge + workbench )
-Horse Carriage 
INTERIOR
-lots of storage
-enchanting table
-alchemy table
-bed
-various of items

download this here at the nexus or at steam . 
either way if u can , plz support us by liking the youtube video / subscribe to our youtube /endorse this mod AND COMMENT THIS MOD IF YOU GOT IDEA\'S FOR NEW ECP\'s !!!!!!!

thx for reading! have fun !
